    "descriptionEn": "UI/UX design focuses on creating intuitive, visually appealing, and user-centered digital experiences for websites and applications. It combines interface aesthetics (UI) with usability, interaction flow, and user research (UX) to ensure products are both functional and enjoyable to use.",
